title: SEC extends decision period for Global X, Franklin Templeton spot Bitcoin ETFs
description:
The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) recently announced that it will extend its decision-making period for two pending spot Bitcoin Exchange Traded Funds (ETFs), according to separate filings made on Nov. 17. The first filing concerns a proposed rule change that would allow Cboe BZX Exchange to list GlobalX’s spot Bitcoin ETF. The proposal […]
